title: Bernoulli’s Principle
question: 有应用到 Bernoulli's Principle / Prinsip Bernoulli 的是
E: Car Lift / Pengangkat Kereta di Bengkel
K: Safety lines near railway tracks / Garisan keselamatan di tepi landasan

question:
根据 Bernoulli's Principle / Prinsip Bernoulli,
Velocity / halaju 越高，pressure / tekanan 越

根据 Bernoulli's Principle / Prinsip Bernoulli,
